data.description: This is a fantastic single-story 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a well-thought-out split bedroom floor plan. Large windows offer plenty of natural light and provide a view of the covered patio, creating a welcoming and bright atmosphere. The kitchen with its granite countertops has plenty of cabinets and counter space. Spray foam insulation. New 8-foot privacy fence ensures that you have a private and secure backyard, perfect for pets, children, or just enjoying your own space.
